
                                      ; Tic Tac toe
                                      ; Guy Fedorkow
                                      ; Sep 26, 2024

                                      ; May 24, 2026 - there's a non-critical bug still in the display of the WW
                                      ; move in FF3 -- the first move is computed by table, and the result is the cell number
                                      ; multiplied by 3.  To display the move properly, I "should" divide the number by 3.

                                      ; Simple game of tic-tac-toe written in Whirlwind assembly code.
                                      ; The game displays on the WW CRT, and can be played with the light gun
                                      ; (As of Sep 26, it's a two-person game, i.e., i alternates X and O plays)

                                      ; Geometry
                                      ; the basic game board is laid out on a 16x16 grid as follows:

                                      ;  cell 0   | cell 1   |  cell 2
                                      ;  @(4,12)  | @(8,12)  |  @(12,12)
                                      ; --------------------------------
                                      ;  cell 3   | cell 4   |  cell 5
                                      ;  @(4,8)   | @(8,8)   |  @(12,8)
                                      ; --------------------------------
                                      ;  cell 6   | cell 7   |  cell 8
                                      ;  @(4,4)   | @(8,4)   |  @(12,4)

                                      ;----------- old layout ----------
                                      ;  cell 6   | cell 7   |  cell 8
                                      ;  @(4,12)  | @(8,12)  |  @(12,12)
                                      ; --------------------------------
                                      ;  cell 3   | cell 4   |  cell 5
                                      ;  @(4,8)   | @(8,8)   |  @(12,8)
                                      ; --------------------------------
                                      ;  cell 0   | cell 1   |  cell 2
                                      ;  @(4,4)   | @(8,4)   |  @(12,4)
                                      ;-------------------------------

                                      .org 0
                                zero:
@0000:000000                 const_0: .word 0                  ; @@WrittenBy apc_table_ts upc_table_ts a0634 apm_copy_dst a0723 igb_table_ts a1452 a1505 a1710 a1727 a1754 a1772 a2041 a2047 ReadBy a0053 ca_addr a0171 dd_y_arg dd_x_arg dc_y_arg dc_x_arg dn_y_arg dn_x1_arg dw_y_arg dw_x_arg dt_y_arg dt_x_arg lgh_x1_arg lgh_y1_arg apc_ca0 upc_ca0 a0607 a0625 a0635 apm_copy_src a0654 a0664 a0673 a0724 a0741 itw_st_ca a0754 itw_cell_ts a0763 a0772 a1000 itw_inc_gb a1111 a1127 a1165 iML_bptr rd_brd1 rd_brd2 a1331 rd_brd3 a1341 a1355 a1373 a1411 a1421 a1424 a1451 a1504 a1636 a1643 a1653 a1664 a1673 a1704 a1711 a1712 a1737 a1750 a1755 a2000 a2001 a2027 a2035 a2152 a2156 a2357 a2371 a2414 a2417 JumpedToBy gb_state_sp a0174 a0344 a0361 a0403 a0424 a0446 a0465 a0504 a0514 light_gun_cell_hit_ret a0565 a0616 a0636 a0725 a0726 a1041 a1135 a1313 a1347 a1432 a1464 a1513 a2004 a2071 a2164 a2423
